# SHS Alma Mater AI Chatbot

This project is an AI-powered chatbot created to assist students, visitors, and alumni of our Senior High School alma mater. The chatbot is designed to provide quick information about the school, such as academic programs, announcements, admission details, and frequently asked questions.

## Project Purpose

The goal of this project is to develop a simple web-based chatbot that can answer common inquiries related to the school and help users easily access important information.

## System Overview 

The chatbot system is built using the following technologies:

* Frontend: HTML, CSS, JavaScript (hosted on GitHub Pages)
* Backend: Vercel serverless functions
* AI Model: Google AI Studio (Gemini API)

## How It Works

1. The user types a question in the chatbot interface.
2. The message is sent to the backend server hosted on Vercel.
3. The backend processes the request and sends it to the Gemini AI API.
4. The AI generates a response and sends it back to the chatbot interface.

## Project Status

This project is currently under development as part of an academic activity.

## Author

Developed by a student from Technological University of the Philippines – Manila (TUP).
